<span class='line-number'>29</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">h1</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="no">Gold</span> <span class="no">Subscription</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="sr">/h1&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">&lt;%= form_tag subscriptions_path do %&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">  &lt;%= label_tag :email %&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">  &lt;%= text_field_tag :email %&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">  &lt;%= hidden_field_tag :plan_id, 101 %&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">  &lt;script</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">    src=&quot;https:/</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">checkout</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">stripe</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">com</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">v2</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">checkout</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">js</span><span class="s2">&quot; class=&quot;</span><span class="n">stripe</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">button</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-key=&lt;%= Rails.configuration.stripe[:publishable_key] %&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-name=&quot;</span><span class="no">Stripe</span> <span class="no">Tutorial</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-description=&quot;</span><span class="no">Gold</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-currency=&quot;</span><span class="n">usd</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-image=&quot;</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">128</span><span class="n">x128</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">png</span><span class="s2">&quot;&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">  &lt;/script&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">&lt;% end %&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">&lt;h1&gt;Silver Subscription&lt;/h1&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">&lt;%= form_tag subscriptions_path do %&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">  &lt;%= label_tag :email %&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">  &lt;%= text_field_tag :email %&gt;&lt;br&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">  &lt;%= hidden_field_tag :plan_id, 102 %&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">  &lt;script</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    src=&quot;</span><span class="ss">https</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="sr">//</span><span class="n">checkout</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">stripe</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">com</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">v2</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">checkout</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">js</span><span class="s2">&quot; class=&quot;</span><span class="n">stripe</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">button</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-key=&lt;%= Rails.configuration.stripe[:publishable_key] %&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-name=&quot;</span><span class="no">Stripe</span> <span class="no">Tutorial</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-description=&quot;</span><span class="no">Silver</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-currency=&quot;</span><span class="n">usd</span><span class="s2">&quot;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">    data-image=&quot;</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="mi">128</span><span class="n">x128</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">png</span><span class="s2">&quot;&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">  &lt;/script&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="s2">&lt;% end %&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>Here, we use the <code>form_tag</code> instead of the normal <code>form_for</code> because we are using Stripe checkout to handle our credit card data and submit the form. We also use a <code>hidden_field_tag</code> to hold the id for our different plans. The plan ids correspond to the ids we set up while creating plans from the Stripe dashboard.</p>

<p>Thats it! You can now sign users up for subscriptions using Stripe.</p>

